parameters.name: BX_SC
parameters.description:
X component of the magnetic field in IRC        
    (despun spacecraft) coordinates.

parameters.name: BY_SC
parameters.description:
Y component of the magnetic field in IRC        
    (despun spacecraft) coordinates.

parameters.name: BZ_SC
parameters.description:
Z component of the magnetic field in IRC        
    (despun spacecraft) coordinates.

parameters.name: AVG_CON
parameters.description:
Optimal averager decimate constant (sample rate)
   in units of spacecraft major frames (1 RIM ~ 60 2/3 seconds).

parameters.name: ROTOR RIGHT ASCENSION
parameters.description: Rotor right ascension in EME-50 coordinates.

parameters.name: T
parameters.description:
Delta twist angle. The difference between the   
   rotor twist angles in EME-50 coordinates and ECL-50 coordinates.
